* '''[[秘境探險：黃金城秘寶|秘境探險：黃金城秘寶]]'''（2007）
:《秘境探險》第一部由索尼於2006年洛杉磯[[電子娛樂展|E3展]]上發布，<ref>{{Cite web| url = http://www.gry-online.pl/S013.asp?ID=26063| title = Konferencja Sony dobiegła końca – jak prezentuje się PS3?| accessdate = 2012-08-09| author = Jiker| date = 2006-05-09| publisher = GRY-OnLine| language = pl| archive-date = 2016-03-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304100034/http://www.gry-online.pl/S013.asp?ID=26063| dead-url = no}}</ref>但直到2007年2月它的標題才被公佈。<ref>{{Cite web| url = http://www.gry-online.pl/S013.asp?ID=31608| title = Screenshot 3D prezentujący nową grę ze studia Naughty Dog| accessdate = 2012-08-09| author = Basza| date = 2007-02-21| publisher = GRY-OnLine| language = pl| archive-date = 2016-03-04| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304233652/http://www.gry-online.pl/S013.asp?ID=31608| dead-url = no}}</ref>本作在歐洲於2007年12月7日發行，幾乎是在美國的三週之後。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gry-online.pl/S016.asp?ID=7214|title=Uncharted: Fortuna Drake’a|publisher=GRY-OnLine|language=pl|accessdate=2012-01-19|archive-date=2017-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170609012020/http://www.gry-online.pl/S016.asp?ID=7214|dead-url=no}}</ref>本作包含各種不同類型的玩法：利用掩體進行駁火、<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gry-online.pl/S020.asp?ID=4629|title=Uncharted: Fortuna Drake’a|author=Cisek|date=2007-12-21|publisher=GRY-OnLine|language=pl|accessdate=2012-01-20|archive-date=2022-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220115215058/https://www.gry-online.pl/S020.asp?ID=4629|dead-url=no}}</ref>近戰、<ref>{{Cite web| url = http://gamerlimit.com/2009/02/gamer-limit-review-uncharted-drakes-fortune/| title = Gamer Limit Review: Uncharted: Drake’s Fortune| accessdate = 2012-08-08| author = Marcos L| date = 2009-02-19| publisher = gamerlimit.com| language = en| archive-date = 2015-03-20| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150320232025/http://gamerlimit.com/2009/02/gamer-limit-review-uncharted-drakes-fortune/| dead-url = no}}</ref>攀爬、在岩石或建築物間跳躍，和與環境互動以解決謎題。<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://archive.is/jQMJE | title = Uncharted: Drake’s Fortune Review| accessdate = 2017-05-12| date = 2007-11-20| publisher = gametrailers.com| language = en}}</ref>此外，玩家還有有機會操作吉普車、水上摩托車及反坦克炮。<ref>{{Cite web| url = http://www.gram.pl/gra_8A3eG,1_Uncharted_Drake_8217s_Fortune.html| title = Uncharted: Fortuna Drake’a| accessdate = 2012-08-08| publisher = gram.pl| language = pl| archive-date = 2022-01-22| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220122194030/https://www.gram.pl/gra_8A3eG,1_Uncharted_Drake_8217s_Fortune.html| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web| url = http://www.thunderboltgames.com/reviews/article/uncharted-drakes-fortune-review-for-ps3.html| title = Uncharted: Drake’s Fortune| accessdate = 2012-08-08| author = Ben Philpott| date = 2008-01-08| publisher = thunderboltgames.com| language = en| archive-date = 2012-11-06| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121106001354/http://thunderboltgames.com/reviews/article/uncharted-drakes-fortune-review-for-ps3.html| dead-url = yes}}</ref>直到2012年8月，本作已售出425萬份。<ref>{{Cite web| url = http://www.vgchartz.com/game/12778/uncharted-drakes-fortune/| title = Uncharted: Fortuna Drake’a| accessdate = 2012-08-10| publisher = vgchartz.com| language = en| archive-date = 2021-12-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211203114830/https://www.vgchartz.com/game/12778/uncharted-drakes-fortune/| dead-url = no}}</ref>

* '''[[秘境探險2：盜亦有道|秘境探險2：盜亦有道]]'''（2009）
:2008年9月，在法國雜誌《{{tsl|en|PSM3|PlayStation 3 Magazine}}》的版面中，頑皮狗副總裁克里斯多福·巴雷斯塔（Christophe Balestra）證實了第一部續作的開發。<ref>{{Cite web| url = http://www.gry-online.pl/S013.asp?ID=43154| title = Francuski PlayStation 3 Magazine donosi – Uncharted 2 nadciąga| accessdate = 2012-07-25| author = Jiker| date = 2008-09-30| publisher = gry-online.pl| language = pl| archive-date = 2016-08-14| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160814132527/http://www.gry-online.pl/S013.asp?ID=43154| dead-url = no}}</ref>2008年12月，遊戲副標題《盜亦有道》被曝光，並發佈了第一支預告片<ref>{{Cite web| url = http://www.gry-online.pl/S013.asp?ID=44166| title = Nathan Drake podąży śladami Marco Polo w Uncharted 2| accessdate = 2012-07-25| author = Szymon Liebert| date = 2008-12-02| publisher = gry-online.pl| language = pl| archive-date = 2016-08-14| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160814152013/http://www.gry-online.pl/S013.asp?ID=44166| dead-url = no}}</ref>。遊戲玩法比前作更豐富：在直升機與坦克的圍追堵截下逃跑、在行駛中的卡車間跳躍、與夥伴艾琳娜一起追趕一輛越野車、在火車上與敵人交戰。<ref name="IGN1">{{Cite web| url = http://uk.ps3.ign.com/articles/102/1026373p1.html| title = Uncharted 2: Among Thieves Review| accessdate = 2012-07-24| author = Chris Roper| date = 2009-09-18| publisher = uk.ps3.ign.com| language = en| archive-date = 2012-05-29| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120529120509/http://uk.ps3.ign.com/articles/102/1026373p1.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>本作加入多人模式，玩家可以與電腦控制的角色競爭或合作。<ref name="IGN4">{{Cite web| url = http://uk.ps3.ign.com/articles/102/1026373p4.html| title = Uncharted 2: Among Thieves Review| accessdate = 2012-07-24| author = Chris Roper| date = 2009-09-18| publisher = uk.ps3.ign.com| language = en| archive-date = 2012-02-10| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120210003227/http://uk.ps3.ign.com/articles/102/1026373p4.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>此外，本作還發布了四個DLC，以擴展多人遊戲的可能性。<ref>{{Cite web| url = http://www.gry-online.pl/dodatki-i-dlc-do-gry.asp?ID=8973| title = Dodatki i DLC do gry Uncharted 2: Among Thieves| accessdate = 2012-07-24| publisher = gry-online.pl| language = pl| archive-date = 2022-01-22| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220122194036/https://www.gry-online.pl/dodatki-i-dlc-do-gry.asp?ID=8973| dead-url = no}}</ref>直到2011年12月，本作已售出490萬份。<ref>{{Cite web| url = http://www.jp.playstation.com/info/release/nr_20111004_uncharted3.html| title = PlayStation®3専用ソフトウェア『アンチャーテッド –砂漠に眠るアトラ ティス-』PR企画 “ゲームをドラマにする！？”『アンチャTV～超冒険的新感覚テレビ』 テレビ東京にて本日１０月３日より放送開始！| accessdate = 2012-08-02| publisher = jp.playstation.com| language = ja| archive-date = 2016-03-03| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215935/http://www.jp.playstation.com/info/release/nr_20111004_uncharted3.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>

