lming-delay-tom-holland-updates/ |title='Uncharted' Movie Shut Down On Tom Holland's First Day Of Shooting |last=Al-Ghamdi |first=Adbullah |work=Screen Rant |date=April 1, 2020 |access-date=April 1, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200401221551/https://screenrant.com/uncharted-movie-filming-delay-tom-holland-updates/ |archive-date=April 1, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>卻因[[嚴重特殊傳染性肺炎疫情|COVID-19疫情]]於三月中旬中斷。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2020/03/sony-uncharted-coronavirus-production-stop-1202884791/ |title=Sony Puts Pause On 'Uncharted' Production Amid Coronavirus Fears |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |first=Amanda |last=N'Duka |date=March 16, 2020 |access-date=March 17, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200317005842/https://deadline.com/2020/03/sony-uncharted-coronavirus-production-stop-1202884791/ |archive-date=March 17, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>有人猜測7月15日將恢復拍攝，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.digitalspy.com/movies/a33320505/tom-holland-uncharted-filming-starts/|title=Tom Holland confirms that 'Uncharted' has finally started filming|last=Warner|first=Sam|work=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|date=July 15, 2020|access-date=July 15, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715164856/https://www.digitalspy.com/movies/a33320505/tom-holland-uncharted-filming-starts/|archive-date=July 15, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>索尼影業澄清雖尚未恢復拍攝，他們正在進行準備，期望電影製作能盡快開始。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://comicbook.com/gaming/news/uncharted-movie-sony-production-has-not-yet-started/|title='Uncharted' Movie: Sony Confirms Production Has Not Yet Started|last=Deschamps|first=Marc|website=Comicbook.com|date=July 15, 2020|access-date=July 15, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715203615/https://comicbook.com/gaming/news/uncharted-movie-sony-production-has-not-yet-started/|archive-date=July 15, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>電影於7月20日在[[德國|德國]]恢復拍攝。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://link.hollywoodreporter.com/view/518d565b191b2a646dbe685ccgu8x.gag/d9b2029a|title='Uncharted' Back on the Map |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=July 17, 2020 |access-date=July 17, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717225512/https://link.hollywoodreporter.com/view/518d565b191b2a646dbe685ccgu8x.gag/d9b2029a |archive-date=July 17, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.thewrap.com/uncharted-with-tom-holland-mark-wahlberg-expected-to-resume-production-in-germany-monday/ |title='Uncharted' With Tom Holland, Mark Wahlberg Expected to Resume Production in Germany Monday |last=Welk |first=Brian |website=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]] |date=July 17, 2020 |access-date=July 18, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718011429/https://www.thewrap.com/uncharted-with-tom-holland-mark-wahlberg-expected-to-resume-production-in-germany-monday/ |archive-date=July 18, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>8月5日，[[安東尼奧·班德拉斯|班德拉斯]]在檢測出COVID-19陽性後暫時離開劇組，<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.thewrap.com/antonio-banderas-celebrates-60th-birthday-in-quarantine-after-positive-coronavirus-test/ |title=Antonio Banderas Celebrates 60th Birthday in Quarantine After Positive Coronavirus Test |website=[[TheWrap|TheWrap]] |first=Brian |last=Welk |date=August 10, 2020 |access-date=August 14, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814070312/https://www.thewrap.com/antonio-banderas-celebrates-60th-birthday-in-quarantine-after-positive-coronavirus-test/ |archive-date=August 14, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>，並在八月下旬痊癒後回到劇組。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2020/film/global/antonio-banderas-coronavirus-2-1234749085/ |title='Pain and Glory' Star Antonio Banderas Recovers From Coronavirus |website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |publisher=[[Penske_Media_Corporation|Penske Media Corporation]] |last=Ramachandran |first=Naman |date=August 26, 2020 |access-date=September 11, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200830182341/https://variety.com/2020/film/global/antonio-banderas-coronavirus-2-1234749085/ |archive-date=August 30, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>9月16日，拍攝移往柏林並公開劇照。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://movieweb.com/uncharted-set-photos-tom-holland-mark-wahlberg/ |title='Uncharted' Set Photos Bring First Look at Tom Holland & Mark Wahlberg |website=[[MovieWeb|MovieWeb]] |last=Fuge |first=Jon |date=September 16, 2020 |access-date=September 17, 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917214149/https://movieweb.com/uncharted-set-photos-tom-holland-mark-wahlberg/ |archive-date=September 17, 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref>2020年10月29日電影殺青。<ref>{{Cite web |last=Bishop |first=Rollin |date=October 29, 2020 |title='Uncharted' Movie Officially Wraps Filming |url=https://comicbook.com/gaming/news/uncharted-movie-wrap-tom-holland/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029144038/https://comicbook.com/gaming/news/uncharted-movie-wrap-tom-holland/ |archive-date=October 29, 2020 |access-date=November 2, 2020 |website=Comicbook}}</ref>

*'''{{tsl|en|Uncharted Live Action Fan Film|粉絲自製電影}}'''
:2018年7月，導演{{tsl|en|Allan Ungar|艾倫·安格爾}}發佈了一部15分鐘非官方改編微電影，由[[奈森·菲利安|奈森·菲利安]]飾演奈森·德瑞克並已為該角色宣傳多年。此片收穫大量好評，尤其是菲利安的表演，以及{{tsl|en|Over-the-shoulder shot|越肩視角}}所呈現出類似射擊遊戲的動作場景。本片尚有[[史帝芬·朗_(演員)|史帝芬·朗]]飾演維克·蘇利文、{{tsl|en|Mircea Monroe|莫西婭・夢露}}飾演伊蓮娜·費雪、{{tsl|en|Ernie Reyes Jr.|小厄尼・雷耶斯}}及{{tsl|en|Geno Segers|吉諾·席格斯}}。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.inverse.com/article/47068-nathan-fillion-stars-in-uncharted-fan-film |title=Nathan Fillion Isn't Even the Best Thing About This 'Uncharted' Fan Film |website=Inverse |last=Francisco |first=Eric |date=July 16, 2018 |access-date=July 16, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180716224218/https://www.inverse.com/article/47068-nathan-fillion-stars-in-uncharted-fan-film |archive-date=July 16, 2018 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theverge.com/2018/7/16/17576712/nathan-fillion-uncharted-nathan-drake-fan-film |title=Nathan Fillion stars as Nathan Drake in what might be film's only good video game adaptation |website=The Verge |last=Stephen |first=Bijan |date=July 16, 2018 |access-date=July 16, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180716185350/https://www.theverge.com/2018/7/16/17576712/nathan-fillion-uncharted-nathan-drake-fan-film |archive-date=July 16, 2018 |url-status=live}}</ref>本片收穫的評價引發關於官方電影原訂計畫是否受到影響的猜測。頑皮狗副總裁[[尼爾·德魯克曼|尼爾·德魯克曼]]在[[Twitter|Twitter]]為該短片送出一個愛心貼圖，電影導演[[薛恩·李維|薛恩·李維]]亦表示稱讚。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://screenrant.com/uncharted-shawn-levy-praises-nathan-fillion-fan-film/ |title=Uncharted Movie Director Praises Nathan Fillion Fan Film |website=Screen Rant |last=Christopher |first=Fiduccia |date=July 27, 2018 |access-date=July 27, 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180728095502/https://screenrant.com/uncharted-shawn-levy-praises-nathan-fillion-fan-film/ |archive-date=July 28, 2018 |url-status=live}}</ref>

